{"tid":653658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter現漏洞　 促全球逾三億用戶改密碼","createTime":"2018-05-05T02:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T02:49:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f245efd2265fc42a1450373c46b1a3f8ebce63d0","tid":653658,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180505/20381811?_ga=2.101725313.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381811%3F_ga%3D2.101725313.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&d=NtOywCjt9gxtgongQE2YADM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=c9f9404a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20381811%3F_ga%3D2.101725313.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171&h=c24ecf8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180505/20381811?_ga=2.101725313.1018314744.1525409067-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年05月05日 <br />\n<br />\nTwitter現漏洞　<br />\n促全球逾三億用戶改密碼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180505/large/05la6p05new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180505%2Flarge%2F05la6p05new.jpg&h=70c35685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Twitter承認發現保安漏洞。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【綜合報道】社交網站Twitter前日承認發現保安漏洞，導致有用戶的密碼在未經加密下儲存在內部系統。Twitter馬上修正漏洞，並建議全數3.36億用戶更改密碼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n密碼未加密隱蔽<br />\n<br />\nTwitter首席科技官阿格拉沃爾（Parag Agrawal）撰文解釋事件。他表示，根據慣常做法，Twitter在用戶設密碼後，會利用加密技術把密碼隱蔽，以防公司內部人員看到。然而，一項程式錯誤使系統儲存未經隱蔽的密碼。Twitter發現漏洞後，已把所有涉事密碼刪除，並採取措施防止重蹈覆轍。未知有多少用戶受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n阿格拉沃爾為事件致歉，強調「我們調查後，未發現數據遭入侵或濫用」。Twitter行政總裁多爾西（Jack Dorsey）表示：「最重要的是，我們要在這次內部錯誤中開誠佈公。」Twitter又向用戶建議多項保護賬戶的方法，包括修改其他使用相同密碼的賬戶、使用雙重認證保安系統，以及為不同賬戶設定難以被猜中兼不重複的密碼。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/《今日美國》網站  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n美容雜誌遭冒名促銷　報警無下文<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n自己工程自己投　法團主席惹質疑"},{"pid":"4f09aca34ac347e363ffc976bf102e5a8d6f5618","tid":653658,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/G5oyVr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FG5oyVr.gif&h=feafc0ba&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}